reviewText: My son is almost 3 and he LOVES Super WHY!  This show is so great for preschool kids who enjoy interactive story lines.  It's helpful with letters and reading and the characters are a modern day fairy tale and they retell the stories we grew up with!  Great Buy.  We have a number of the Super WHY products including the other dvd.
